title: Bike Light Set Front Light with Taillight USB Rechargeable Easy to Install 3 Modes Bicycle Accessories for the Bicycle Road MTB
description:
Bike Light Set Front Light with Taillight USB Rechargeable Easy to Install 3 Modes Bicycle Accessories for the Bicycle Road MTB

Notice:
When you need to turn on the tail light, you need to press the button for a long time. You can try to perform this operation, if you have any questions, please feel free to contact us, we will solve the problem for you in time!

Features:
Front Light (USB Rechargeable):
3 Working Modes: High-Medium-Strobe
Power Source: 800mAh Li-Poly Battery
Charging Time: Approx.3hours
Rear Light (USB Rechargeable):
Bulb Type: LEDs
Brightness: 15 lumens
Front Light Color: Black
Mounting Placement: Bicycle Seat Post
Suitable Tube Diameter: Approx.12-32mm

4 modes: Long Bright, slow flash, explosion flash and strobe.
Tail Light (USB Rechargeable):
Material: PC+ABS
Light Source: XPE 3W LED
Tail Lights Color: Red
Output (Maximum): 300lm
Lighting Distance: 30-50meters at night

SET1:918 Red Tail Lights OPP
SET2:928 Red Tail Lights OPP
SET3:2255 Front Lights OPP

SET5:2255 Front Lights +928 Red Tail Lights OPP

title: Lightweight Electric Dirt Bike for Kids, 150/250W Up to 10/12MPH, 24V Detachable Battery, Hand-Operated Dual Brakes ElectricBike
description:
Lightweight Electric Dirt Bike for Kids, 150/250W Up to 10/12MPH, 24V Detachable Battery, Hand-Operated Dual Brakes ElectricBike
  • Exclusively Crafted for Young Riders: This super light electric-powered motorcycle features a professional variable-speed twist throttle for speed modulation. Not only does it serve as a traditional balance bike, but it also offers an off-road experience, enhancing kids' balance and coordination skills. Two speed settings: a beginner-friendly 5 mph mode and an advanced mode reaching up to 10 mph.
  • Sleek and Durable Construction: Built with a robust aluminum alloy frame and finished with a polished paint job, this balance bike's aesthetic appeal is undeniable. Weighing a mere 23.2 lbs, the integration of a 24V 150W brushless motor, paired with an all-inclusive transmission chain, ensures efficient power transmission for a safe and reliable riding experience.
  • Long-lasting Battery with Rapid Charging: The AIII is powered by a 24V 2.6AH lithium-ion battery, offering 40-70 min of run time. Enclosed within the ebike's metallic frame, this detachable battery can be replaced within a minute and comes with a protective cover. A rapid 2-3 hour charging period, coupled with a throttle-mounted LED display, makes battery management a breeze.
  • Safety with Versatility in Terrain: Specially designed brake lever for kids with rear drum brake, it ensures children can stop the motorbike efficiently. The 12-inch inflatable rubber composite tires guarantee excellent traction, grip, and shock absorption across varied terrains, allowing young riders to confidently explore their surroundings.
  • Customizable and Growth-accommodating Design: Ideal for kids aged 3-6 years, our electric dirt bike boasts an adjustable seat height to grow with the rider. Additionally, each electric bike includes a number and name board kit, enabling young riders to personalize their AIII with their chosen race number and name.

title: Ridstar Q20/Q20Pro Electric Bike 2000W Powerful Motor 52V40AH Oil Brake 20*4.0inch Fat Tire Ebike Mountain Snow Electric Bicycle
description:
New Ridstar-Q20 electric bike
Q: Can the battery be removed?
A: Yes, the battery can be taken out from the outside

Q20 EBIKE

The Q20 e-bike is a comfortable e-bike developed by our company and suitable for people of 158cm-195cm in height. The wide seat allows you to ride with children, equipped with a front hydraulic shock absorber and a central cushioning device, equipped with the original bike waterproof bag, red oil disc brakes to highlight the fashion elements, equipped with Shimano 7-speed transmission, so that there is no obstacle ahead of you.

Actual weight: 34kg

Tire size: 20*4.0
Display: LCD
Maximum speed >50km/h
Endurance 80km
Slope>35°

Battery type: lithium battery
